==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: 18,000 [[里|li]].

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: shí wàn bā qiān lĭ

===Idiom===

'''[[十]][[萬]][[八]][[千]][[里]]'''

# Used to describe a great distance.

#: ''[[偶]][[從]]'''十萬八千里'''[[的]][[地方]][[回來]][[了]].'' 

# Used to describe a huge difference between two things.

#: ''[[想像]][[真]][[的]][[會]][[離]][[事实|事實]]'''十萬八千里'''[[的]]！'' 

===Alternate forms===
[[十万八千里]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

